    'What are the peak call hours and how should we staff accordingly?',
    'Which patients are at highest fall risk based on response times?',
    'Show me a chart comparing response times across providers',
    'What language barriers exist in our unit and how can we address them?',
    'Identify the top 3 quality improvement opportunities from the last 30 days',
    'Generate research hypotheses I can use for an IRB submission',
    'Where can I find a downloadable QI report?',
    'How does night shift compare to day shift for response times?',
